* Editor's note: This live event has ended. You may watch a recording above. JOHANNESBURG - President Cyril Ramaphosa is expected to reply to the Parliamentary debate on his post-COVID-19 economic recovery plan.
The president presented the Economic Reconstruction and Recovery Plan last week. WATCH: Ramaphosa unveils economic recovery plan He said government will set aside R100-billion to ensure the strategy is realised. The plan is the result of extensive deliberation between government and its social partners, including business and labour.